          <div class="sub-card">
            <div class="sub-card-top">
              <span class="sub-card-num">02</span>
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d91e45" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="8" cy="21" r="1"/><circle cx="19" cy="21" r="1"/><path d="M2.05 2.05h2l2.66 12.42a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.58h9.78a2 2 0 0 0 1.95-1.57l1.65-7.43H5.12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="sub-card-title">Results-Driven E-Commerce</h3>
            <p class="sub-card-tagline">Your Online Store, Built to Sell</p>
            <p class="sub-card-desc">A good-looking store means nothing if it doesn't sell. We build e-commerce websites where every page is designed to earn trust, remove friction, and close the sale.</p>            <ul class="sub-card-features">
              <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d91e45" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:4px;"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span><strong>Sells while you sleep</strong><br/><small style="color:#6b7280;font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.5;">24/7 automated sales</small></span></li>
