                  <summary>How much does a website cost? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
